name: ElectDrone
descriptions: An Electro special drone designed for long distance flight and comes with a built in camera that last for 48 hours

name: PlayStation 5
descriptions: The latest Sony PlayStation introduced in November 2020. Powered by an eight-core AMD Zen 2 CPU and custom AMD Radeon GPU, the PS5 is offered in two models: with and without a 4K Blu-ray drive. Supporting a 120Hz video refresh, the PS5 is considerably more powerful than the PS4 and PS4 Pro.

name: XBOX One
descriptions: The Xbox One is a home video game console developed by Microsoft. Announced in May 2013, it is the successor to Xbox 360 and the third base console in the Xbox series of video game consoles.

name: NEW YEARS SPECIAL!!!
descriptions: This is a special that comes with a Xbox One S series, PlayStation 4, SteelSeries Arctis 9 and Switch joy con

name: DJI Air 2S
descriptions: A drone that is equipped with a 1-inch image sensor and large 2.4Î¼m pixels, DJI Air 2S is capable of 5.4K/30fps and 4K/60fps video. Capture any moment with the rich clarity and authentic color tones it deserves.

name: DroneNim
descriptions: A drone that is built for that specific camera angle that you are always lookig for and has a slim design to be easily transported and handle.

name: Phantom 4 Pro
descriptions: Featuring a 1-inch CMOS sensor that can shoot 4K/60fps videos and 20MP photos, the Phantom 4 Pro V2.0 grants filmmakers absolute creative freedom. The OcuSync 2.0 HD transmission system ensures stable connectivity and reliability, five directions of obstacle sensing ensures additional safety, and a dedicated remote controller with a built-in screen grants even greater precision and control. [1] A wide array of intelligent features makes flying that much easier. The Phantom 4 Pro V2.0 is a complete aerial imaging solution, designed for the professional creator.

name: Estate Cruiser - 60V 2000W Lithium Electric Scooter
descriptions: The ultimate in golf scooter comfort and style! (Golf bag holder included)The Estate Cruiser is propelled to speeds of 50Km per hour by a 2000W electric hub motor. Powered by a 60 volt, 15AH lithium battery, the cruiser is capable of coving distances of up to 40Km per charge. This will easily cover 18 holes even at low speeds.The Estate Cruiser has a hill-climbing capability of 25 degrees and maximum rider weight of 200kgs.The quality of our Estate cruisers are excellent and you can expect years of service and fun.

name: Oculus Quest 2/Meta Quest 2
descriptions: The Oculus (or Meta, if you prefer) Quest 2 improves on the original headset in nearly every way possible, and at a more affordable price. It's the best $300 VR headset for newbies and experienced users alike.

name: Valve Index VR Full Kit
descriptions: The Valve Index is the most impressive consumer VR headset we've seen yet, entirely due to its revolutionary, finger-tracking controllers.

name: Nintendo Switch Neon Blue/Neon Red
descriptions: Play anytime, anywhere with anyone. Perfect for multiplayer fun with family and friends. Connect to your tv and play together, or connect the Joy-Con controllers for portable solo or multiplayer gaming. The Nintendo Switch is designed to fit your lifestyle, transforming from a home console to a portable system in a snap. Enjoy immersive real-action HD gaming with the motion controls built into the Joy-Con controllers
